Class OConfigurableStatefulFactory<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.common.factory.OConfigurableStatefulFactory<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:

    V - Instance type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OClusterSelectionFactory, OLocalRecordCacheFactoryImpl

    public class OConfigurableStatefulFactory<K,V>
extends Object
    Configurable stateful factory. New instances are created when newInstance() is called, invoking its default empty constructor.
